text: Lipscomb County is a county in the U.S. state of Texas. In 2020, 3,059 people lived there. The county seat is Lipscomb. ==Geography== The county has a total area of 932 square miles. ==Places== ===City=== * Higgins ===Towns=== * Lipscomb (county seat) * Booker * Darrouzett * Follett ==References== Category:Texas counties
title: Lipscomb County, Texas
